<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>搜索与推荐 - 分类 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/categories/%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E4%B8%8E%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90/</link><description>搜索与推荐 - 分类 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ksmaple.github.io/categories/%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E4%B8%8E%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Elasticsearch核心</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B1%82/%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E4%B8%8E%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90/elasticsearch%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B1%82/%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E4%B8%8E%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90/elasticsearch%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="elasticsearch核心">Elasticsearch核心</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：Elasticsearch基于Lucene实现分布式搜索，通过倒排索引加速全文检索，通过分片和副本实现水平扩展和高可用，理解索引、分片、映射和查询DSL是使用ES的基础。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="elasticsearch基于lucene构建通过分片分布式存储通过倒排索引实现高性能全文搜索">Elasticsearch基于Lucene构建，通过分片分布式存储，通过倒排索引实现高性能全文搜索</h2>
<h3 id="核心概念索引文档映射分片">核心概念：索引、文档、映射、分片</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>概念</th>
          <th>说明</th>
          <th>类比关系型数据库</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>Index</td>
          <td>索引，文档的集合</td>
          <td>Database</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>Document</td>
          <td>文档，一条JSON数据</td>
          <td>Row</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>Mapping</td>
          <td>映射，字段类型定义</td>
          <td>Schema</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>Type</td>
          <td>类型（7.0+已废弃）</td>
          <td>Table</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>Shard</td>
          <td>分片，数据的最小单元</td>
          <td>Partition</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>Replica</td>
          <td>副本，分片的复制</td>
          <td>Replica</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">索引结构：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Index: products
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">├── Primary Shard 0 (Node-1)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   └── Replica 0 (Node-2)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">├── Primary Shard 1 (Node-2)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   └── Replica 1 (Node-3)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">├── Primary Shard 2 (Node-3)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">│   └── Replica 2 (Node-1)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">└── Primary Shard 3 (Node-1)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    └── Replica 3 (Node-2)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">路由：shard = hash(routing) % number_of_primary_shards
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">routing默认是文档_id</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="倒排索引与文本分析">倒排索引与文本分析</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">文本分析流程（Analysis）：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">原始文本: &#34;The quick brown foxes jumped!&#34;
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Character Filter: 去除HTML、替换字符
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Tokenizer: 分词 → [the, quick, brown, foxes, jumped]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Token Filter: 
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - Lowercase: [the, quick, brown, foxes, jumped]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - Stop words: [quick, brown, foxes, jumped]（去除the）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - Stemming: [quick, brown, fox, jump]（foxes→fox, jumped→jump）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">存入倒排索引</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
